![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/93aa6e64-7910-4464-b235-0c9f10187085/Screenshot_20250217_173817.jpg?format=original)

*   ## AJ STYLES DEF. DOMINIK MYSTERIO
    

After several interference attempts by Carlito. AJ Styles gets the win.

Bron Breakker attempts to sneak attack AJ Styles but AJ dodged and Bron took out Dominik instead. AJ attacks Bron and then goes to grab the Intercontinental Championship but Bron takes his belt and leaves.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/08b44767-173f-475d-a4e6-b6a32aaef974/Screenshot_20250217_173854.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f4fa473d-5373-493a-99f9-0856ea9b1782/20250217_174645.jpg?format=original)

Julius Creed has been announced as a coach on Daniel Cormier’s The Ultimate Fighter team

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/53b32c1f-90fe-4992-b5f4-caa4e564a687/Messenger_creation_489354890668390.jpeg?format=original)

*   ## **_DAKOTA KAI DEF. IVY NILE_**
    

It appears Dakota Kai will earn a shot at the Intercontinental Championship against Lyra Valkyria. However nothing is made official yet.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/dc1a8b37-455c-4e7b-814e-9307095b0228/20250217_175220.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/56cfa98f-9610-4b34-9663-0f04f9af03fb/Messenger_creation_971686424623960.jpeg?format=original)

"Me performing for you is like reading Shakespeare to a dog."

Gunther says he's tired of wrestling against people who could never even lace his boots. When their match begins at WrestleMania, Gunther wants Jey Uso to know it's going to take place inside of a wrestling ring, not in the crowd.

Gunther then goes up to Michael Cole and Pat McAfee to ask if they think Jey USO really has a chance against him. Pat says he does. Gunther is going to beat on him but Jey USO music hits.

Jey is being held back by security but he breaks loose. He brawls with Gunther until security interferes again. Their brawl continues until Gunther escapes the ring.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/56943bee-277f-451c-9903-6d08a2061350/Messenger_creation_594234610104207.jpeg?format=original)

* * *

