*   ## **_PENTA DEF. PETE DUNNE_**
    

Ludwig Kaiser comes out during the match at one point and only serves as a distraction to Pete Dunne. Penta gets the W, ultimately.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c8a11fe6-5a1f-43b5-abd9-b072fa65dbcb/Messenger_creation_1678953679325530.jpeg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/eaa85c9a-e21f-4876-aea2-bf44cc0397c8/Messenger_creation_1577345096279625.jpeg?format=original)

Jey USO tells Cathy Kelly he feels underestimated. He's going to prove everyone wrong at WrestleMania.

