![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ffa21c73-d89d-479d-b1a0-d5f952af402a/Messenger_creation_1145529937251017.jpeg?format=original)

*   ## **_ELIMINATION CHAMBER QUALIFIER: ROXANNE PEREZ DEF. RAQUEL RODRIGUEZ_**
    

Roxanne Perez gets the win after Bianca Belair and Naomi surprised Liv and Raquel in an attempt to get revenge for Jade Cargill

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/77acfb99-bb1d-46c7-bcb6-39e22962d3bb/Messenger_creation_1403923490589693.jpeg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/27c14d87-24c6-4285-8e28-5e3b7a7e7725/Messenger_creation_7707728459351905.jpeg?format=original)

The New Day is out cutting a promo about how Rey Mysterio sucks the life out of every new Luchadore that comes to WWE.

They're interrupted by LWO who say that New Day sucks. This leads to a brawl that ends when New Day leaves the ring.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d7e10cd1-c927-4bb3-a158-3fd2b4aa3283/Messenger_creation_1363649271478905.jpeg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/dd98ccd5-c960-4802-823f-e04fb9c9b954/Messenger_creation_652913683955232.jpeg?format=original)

## **_ELIMINATION CHAMBER QUALIFIER: SETH ROLLINS DEF. FINN BALOR_**

Excellent match besides a errant moment where Finn Balor did not kick out on time and Rod Zapata had to cover for him.

Seth Rollins enters the Chamber, and all spots are now closed.

The Elimination Chamber is now Seth Rollins vs Drew McIntyre vs CM Punk vs John Cena vs Logan Paul vs Damian Priest

